description.en:
SpideyInu is an ERC-20 token named in homage to the world’s most popular superhero doge.

The token features a variable reflection mechanic that provides a standard 2% returns on transactions for traders.

Total token supply is 10 Trillion, total standard tax per transaction (buy & sell) is 10% (variable for community incentives/promotions).

The project team intends SpideyInu to be the principal token in a significant, extended ecosystem including NFTs, a P2E game, and eventual print and animation media releases, working in partnership with key industry leaders.
